## Workspace Structure

Crates

- ğŸ› ï¸ **[`gguppy_core`](crates/gguppy_core/)**
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Implementation of the Grammar of Graphics in `no_std` Rust
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Consumes any DataFrame-like structure implementing the `GGData` trait
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Extensible with any plot types implementing the `GGCapable` trait
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Produces geometric primitives implementing the `DrawablePrim` trait
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Compiles for static desktop display or interactive wasm plots

- ğŸ› ï¸ **[`gguppy_data`](crates/gguppy_data/)**
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Minimalist DataFrame-like `minidf` plottable by `gguppy` in `no_std` Rust
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Features adapters for `arrow` and `arrow2`
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Features adapters for `polars`, `pandas`, and more

- ğŸ› ï¸ **[`arwggplot`](crates/arwggplot/)**
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Minimalist svg backend for `gguppy` in `no_std` Rust
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Features vector backends to svg, eps, and more
  - ğŸ› ï¸ Features raster backends to bmp, png, and more

Module Layout

- **src**
  - [lib.rs](src/lib.rs) - `mod` and `re-export`
  - [prelude.rs](src/prelude.rs) - `use` statements for the entire library

